-1. Install python && python setup tool: https://docs.python-guide.org/starting/install3/linux/ && 
0. Install cmake: https://vitux.com/how-to-install-cmake-on-ubuntu-18-04/
1. Install python dlib: https://gist.github.com/ageitgey/629d75c1baac34dfa5ca2a1928a7aeaf
2. Install brew : /bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"
3. Install cmake: brew install cmake
4. Install face detection python package: pip3 install face_recognition
(5. Install opencv python: pip3 install opencv-python) not really needed
6. Install scikit :pip3 install scikit-learn , pip3 install -U scikit-learn